<section class="product-enhance">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="product-enhance__content">
      <h2>How Roman Shades Enhance Your Space</h2>
      <h3 class="p-subheader">
        Roman shades combine drapery softness with shade functionality, offering
        tailored folds and fabric options for versatile style and comfort.
      </h3>
      <p>
        Crafted from a single fabric panel with hidden rods, Roman shades fold
        into neat pleats when raised. Choose from cord, cordless, or motorized
        systems for beauty and convenience. Smart home integration provides
        effortless control.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-enhance__media container--wide">
      <picture>
        <source
          srcset="/images/product-video.png"
          type="image/png"
          media="(max-width: 1023px)"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/product-video.png"
          alt="Roman shade video"
          width="1024"
          height="576"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

